  ep1: {
    situation: '20 minutes in. Most students have correct answers. But when you look at their books, the working is invisible — Rajan has written almost nothing, Nur has only the final number, Wei Jie has scribbled and erased his steps, and Siti has the right answer with a completely blank working space. You cannot tell how any of them got there.',
    evidence: 'Most students have correct final answers. Almost no one has shown their working. You do not know whether they are reasoning, guessing, or using a method you have not taught.',
    choices: [
      {
        id: 'A',
