        elaboration: 'Project Q1: angles 50° and 60°. (1) What is the third angle? (2) How did you find it? Students write their method on mini-whiteboards or paper before you discuss.',
        theoryKey: 'Two_Step_MCQ',
        tradeoff: 'Reveals the hidden methods quickly — but students who are guessing may struggle to articulate a method, and the public display of methods may embarrass those who cannot explain.'
