      consequence: '20 of 24 students got the correct answer. But only 12 of 24 wrote any steps — and 8 of those wrote "I guessed the sum." Nur wrote "I added them." Rajan wrote "intuition." Wei Jie erased his working before showing you. Siti left the method blank. The correct answers are masking a range of hidden processes — some reasoning, some guessing. 18 minutes remain.',
